WEBVTT

00:03:27.943 --> 00:03:30.010
researching and writing a book.

00:03:31.219 --> 00:03:32.584
My conclusion?

00:03:33.950 --> 00:03:37.267
Racism leads to bad policymaking.

00:03:38.085 --> 00:03:40.410
It's making our economy worse.

00:03:41.387 --> 00:03:45.024
And not just in ways
that disadvantage people of color.

00:03:45.850 --> 00:03:48.731
It turns out it's not a zero sum.

00:03:49.477 --> 00:03:52.929
Racism is bad for white people, too.

00:03:55.951 --> 00:03:57.657
Take, for example,

00:03:57.681 --> 00:04:01.726
America's underinvestment
